{
  "texts": [
    "We present the first wall-to-wall map of land-use following deforestation across Africa covering forest loss from the year 2001 to 2020 (Fig. 2).",
    "The output predicted map is available at a spatial resolution of 5 m, with 15 landuse classes.",
    "The map has a users accuracy of 85%, producers accuracy of 84%, and F1-score of 85% (Fig. 3).",
    "For detailed visualisation, the predicted output map of land use following deforestation is available at this website: https:// rober tnag82. users.",
    "earth engine."
  ]
}